  "detailed_description": "<i>Risk of Rain meets Noita.</i><br><br><strong>Space Bot</strong> is a strategic roguelite where your environment is fully desctructable, and out to get you. Travel with your friendly spaceship as you hunt for 'GELD' on far away and mysterious planets.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123110/extras/088153d8129da2f9324b525aae427195.poster.avif?t=1668665429\" width=628 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123110/extras/088153d8129da2f9324b525aae427195.webm?t=1668665429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123110/extras/088153d8129da2f9324b525aae427195.mp4?t=1668665429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Procedural Planets</strong> Have a different experience each time you play with procedurally generated levels<br></li><li><strong>Unique Enemies</strong> Fight increasingly difficult and creepy enemies as you rush to escape<br></li><li><strong>Find Upgrades</strong> Increase your stats as your progress through the game. The better you play, the more upgrades you can use!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123110/extras/108d29c08ab18d633e3722125b11372d.poster.avif?t=1668665429\" width=628 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123110/extras/108d29c08ab18d633e3722125b11372d.webm?t=1668665429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123110/extras/108d29c08ab18d633e3722125b11372d.mp4?t=1668665429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The longer you stay on a planet, the more enemies will appear and attack you. Try and get your Geld and get out!<br><br>Space Bot is currently in development by Incinious. Let me know your thoughts and suggestions on twitter @Incinious!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123110/extras/a143fe2c50b321a3ca85c77870873b4a.poster.avif?t=1668665429\" width=628 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123110/extras/a143fe2c50b321a3ca85c77870873b4a.webm?t=1668665429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123110/extras/a143fe2c50b321a3ca85c77870873b4a.mp4?t=1668665429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>Inspiration for this game was drawn from:</i><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>OpenLiero-X<br></li><li>Motherload<br></li><li>Binding of Isaac<br></li><li>Risk of Rain<br></li><li>Terraria<br></li><li>Noita</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<i>Risk of Rain meets Noita.</i><br><br><strong>Space Bot</strong> is a strategic roguelite where your environment is fully desctructable, and out to get you. Travel with your friendly spaceship as you hunt for 'GELD' on far away and mysterious planets.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123110/extras/088153d8129da2f9324b525aae427195.poster.avif?t=1668665429\" width=628 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123110/extras/088153d8129da2f9324b525aae427195.webm?t=1668665429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123110/extras/088153d8129da2f9324b525aae427195.mp4?t=1668665429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Procedural Planets</strong> Have a different experience each time you play with procedurally generated levels<br></li><li><strong>Unique Enemies</strong> Fight increasingly difficult and creepy enemies as you rush to escape<br></li><li><strong>Find Upgrades</strong> Increase your stats as your progress through the game. The better you play, the more upgrades you can use!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123110/extras/108d29c08ab18d633e3722125b11372d.poster.avif?t=1668665429\" width=628 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123110/extras/108d29c08ab18d633e3722125b11372d.webm?t=1668665429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123110/extras/108d29c08ab18d633e3722125b11372d.mp4?t=1668665429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The longer you stay on a planet, the more enemies will appear and attack you. Try and get your Geld and get out!<br><br>Space Bot is currently in development by Incinious. Let me know your thoughts and suggestions on twitter @Incinious!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123110/extras/a143fe2c50b321a3ca85c77870873b4a.poster.avif?t=1668665429\" width=628 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123110/extras/a143fe2c50b321a3ca85c77870873b4a.webm?t=1668665429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123110/extras/a143fe2c50b321a3ca85c77870873b4a.mp4?t=1668665429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>Inspiration for this game was drawn from:</i><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>OpenLiero-X<br></li><li>Motherload<br></li><li>Binding of Isaac<br></li><li>Risk of Rain<br></li><li>Terraria<br></li><li>Noita</li></ul>",
